  "texts": [
    "In particular, the SDA transformer process helps capture relationships between all tokens in the sequence, providing a more comprehensive understanding of the context.",
    "This is particularly useful when dealing with long documents or sequences.",
    "November -December 2023 During this period, several updates to LLMs, especially for Copilot, have been released.",
    "In November 2023, researchers from the University of Florida and NVIDIA published a paper for explaining GatorTronGPT [36].",
    "The model has a GPT-3 architecture and was trained on the Pile dataset and de-identified clinical text from the University of Florida."
